><description>由于俄罗斯降低了使用核武器的门槛并向乌克兰发射高超音速弹道导弹，黄金周五将创下近八个月来的最大单周涨幅，而欧元则徘徊在13个月低点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 02:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统将访问图瓦卢、帕劳和马绍尔群岛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-tuvalu-palau-marshall-islands-2024-11-22/</link><description>总统府周五表示，台湾总统赖清德将访问太平洋的图瓦卢、帕劳和马绍尔群岛。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 02:25:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-tuvalu-palau-marshall-islands-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>由于乌克兰战争加剧的焦虑，油价每周上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-intensifying-ukraine-war-increases-supply-risk-2024-11-22/</link><description>随着俄罗斯总统普京警告全球冲突，乌克兰战争愈演愈烈，周五油价延续涨势，每周上涨超过 4%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 02:10:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-intensifying-ukraine-war-increases-supply-risk-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统将访问太平洋盟友，但没有美国过境的详细信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-pacific-island-nation-allies-2024-11-22/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德办公室周五表示，台湾总统赖清德将从本月底开始访问台北在太平洋地区仅存的三个外交盟友，但政府拒绝透露美国过境地点的详细信息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 00:11:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-pacific-island-nation-allies-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>习近平访问摩洛哥并会见王储</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-visits-morocco-meets-with-crown-prince-says-state-media-2024-11-22/</link><description>据国家通讯社MAP报道，中国国家主席习近平周四对摩洛哥进行了短暂访问。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 00:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-visits-morocco-meets-with-crown-prince-says-state-media-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着贸易紧张局势加剧，中国企业寻求美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/corporate-china-seeks-dollars-trade-tensions-rise-2024-11-21/</link><description>由于贸易紧张局势可能会扰乱外汇汇率，中国企业正在储备更多美元，以人民币定价合同，并开放进口额度，以减轻货币风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 23:06:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/corporate-china-seeks-dollars-trade-tensions-rise-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：韧性是游戏的名称，关注日本 CPI</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-21/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 21:52:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构理事会通过伊朗决议，西方推动德黑兰进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-nuclear-watchdogs-35-nation-board-passes-resolution-against-iran-2024-11-21/</link><description>目的是迫使伊朗就对其核活动的新限制进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 21:01:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-nuclear-watchdogs-35-nation-board-passes-resolution-against-iran-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>政府称埃克森集团退出与圭亚那浅水石油区块的谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-mobil-pulls-out-talks-with-guyana-over-shallow-water-oil-block-gov-says-2024-11-21/</link><description>圭亚那副总统周四表示，美国石油巨头埃克森美孚及其合作伙伴已退出与圭亚那政府就勘探和开发浅水石油区块条款进行的谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 20:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-mobil-pulls-out-talks-with-guyana-over-shallow-water-oil-block-gov-says-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>因安全担忧引发 FCC 提议对中国视频门铃制造商处以罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fcc-proposes-fine-chinese-video-doorbell-manufacturer-after-security-concerns-2024-11-21/</link><description>美国联邦通信委员会周四提议对中国视频门铃制造商 Eken 处以近 735,000 美元的罚款，原因是其提供虚假信息并引发安全担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 16:51:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fcc-proposes-fine-chinese-video-doorbell-manufacturer-after-security-concerns-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>美国机构投票启动审查并更新海底电信电缆规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-agency-votes-launch-review-update-undersea-telecommunications-cable-rules-2024-11-21/</link><description>面对日益增长的安全担忧，美国联邦通信委员会周四投票提出了管理海底互联网电缆的新规则，作为对处理几乎所有全球在线流量的链路法规的审查的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 16:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-agency-votes-launch-review-update-undersea-telecommunications-cable-rules-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国指责美国对台政策导致防务领导人未会面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-blames-us-policy-taiwan-defence-leaders-not-meeting-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国国防部指责美国对台湾的立场，导致中国国防部长本周在老挝举行的一次会议上没有与美国国防部长会面。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 14:22:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-blames-us-policy-taiwan-defence-leaders-not-meeting-2024-11-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>